  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bcb\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bc0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0baf \u0bae\u0bcb\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Motorcycle caught fire during petrol theft",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The incident took place on 05th Tuesday at 4 o'clock in the morning at a house in Otamavadi - 01 Seenipodiyar Road under the Vazaichenai Police Division.",
        "The motorcycle caught fire when a thief used a lighter to light it while stealing petrol from a motorcycle parked in front of the house, and the roof, door and windows of the house caught fire.",
        "When the motorcycle caught fire, the thief mistook it for water and poured paint-coating dinner in a bucket on the motorcycle.",
        "The owner of the house said that when the motorcycle was on fire, he got up and brought the fire under control after hearing a cry to get up.",
        "It is noted that the Vazaichenai police are conducting further investigations related to this incident."
      ],
